<p>Margaret Flowers practiced pediatrics for 17 years and currently serves as the codirector of <a href="https://popularresistance.org/">Popular Resistance</a> and the national coordinator of <a href="http://healthoverprofit.org/">Health Over Profit for Everyone</a>. She is an adviser to the board of <a href="https://pnhp.org/">Physicians for a National Health Program</a>.</p>
